(6824, 1, '2014-04-02 21:21:47', '2014-04-02 21:21:47', '<div id="banner" class="cs-header-view"><img alt="internal banner" src="http://dev.edmbiz.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/internal-banner.jpg" width="1160" height="190" /></div>\r\n\r\n<header class="cs-heading-title">\r\n<h2 class="colr cs-section-title">How Can Your Brand Activate?</h2>\r\n</header>\r\n<p>EDMbiz will work with you and your internal teams on creating a custom way to integrate your brand into our programming. Examples include:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Attendee gift bag inclusion</li>\r\n<li>Booths</li>\r\n<li>Charging lounge</li>\r\n<li>Cocktail reception</li>\r\n<li>Coffee/Snack Bar</li>\r\n<li>“Discovery” Room - DJ lessons</li>\r\n<li>EDM Game Lounge</li>\r\n<li>Evening "swim" & cabanas</li>\r\n<li>Green room gifting lounge (presenting)</li>\r\n<li>Green room/VIP activation/seeding</li>\r\n<li>Green room/VIP gift bag</li>\r\n<li>Listening lounge</li>\r\n<li>Luncheon for attendees/VIPs</li>\r\n<li>Meeting room(s) presenting sponsor</li>\r\n<li>Presenting sponsor (other level breakdown)</li>\r\n<li>Social media wall projections</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;<br />&nbsp;<br /></p>\r\n\r\n<header class="cs-heading-title">\r\n<h2 class="colr cs-section-title">2014 EDMbiz Partnership Pricing</h2>\r\n</header>\r\n<p>EDMbiz Presenting Partnership Package - Pricing & Details Available Upon Request </p>\r\n<p>Green Room Presenting Partnership Package - $45,000 </p>\r\n<p>Opening Reception Title Partnership Package - $35,000 </p>\r\n<p>Sandbox Activation - $10,000 and Up </p>\r\n<p>Concourse Activation - $8,000 </p>\r\n<p>Lounge Activation - TBD </p>\r\n<p>Large Expo Booth (Pipe & Drape* - 20x20) - $5,000 </p>\r\n<p>Medium Expo Booth (Pipe & Drape* - 20x10) - $4,000 </p>\r\n<p>Small Expo Booth (Pipe & Drape* - 10x10) - $3,000 </p>\r\n<p>Gift Bag Inclusion (Quantity of 1,000**) - $1,500 </p>\r\n<p>Program Ad - Priced by Size </p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;<br />&nbsp;<br /></p>\r\n\r\n<header class="cs-heading-title